{"tid":299722,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇FUN RUN JJ?","createTime":"2017-06-27T10:11:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-27T18:31:33.000Z","uid":49143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2a40cbf672d70711cbd958323c651f2e39b6fd88","tid":299722,"uid":49143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T10:11:34.000Z","msg":"有冇巴絲有玩開Fun Run，我見其實香港區有唔少玩家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知有冇巴絲有玩開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定係全部都係細佬仔玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平時無聊等人、去廁所冇野做就會玩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每場一分鐘都唔洗，當燒下時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：由第一代玩到第二代，再玩到第三代Run Fun Arena<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eedf8d9af805d8ad204a13ac8af7a99a6f0b871d","tid":299722,"uid":9767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T10:20:00.000Z","msg":"有第三代 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我平時會話自己玩FR2 人地以為我玩緊咩大作 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a58371f1d83698a79f9ca8b9ae17bfe0a48ee0c","tid":299722,"uid":49143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T10:41:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有第三代 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我平時會話自己玩FR2 人地以為我玩緊咩大作 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係呀，有第三代好耐啦<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/27/184111_1ffa095d17ba86094baf7204f5f1b393.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F27%2F184111_1ffa095d17ba86094baf